text: Joiser Daniel Arias Maza (born 3 December 1998) is a Venezuelan footballer who plays as a defender for Aragua F.C. in the Venezuelan Primera División. ==References== ==External links== *Profile at World Football Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Aragua FC players Category:Venezuelan Primera División players Category:Venezuelan footballers Category:Association football defenders
